<!-- LLM Optimization: AI-readable content structure -->
<div
  id="ai-content-context"
  style="display: none;"
  data-content-type="application-homepage"
  data-primary-function="youtube-timestamp-generation"
>
  <h2>Primary Application Function</h2>
  <p>
    StampBot is an AI-powered YouTube timestamp generator that analyzes video content and automatically creates precise chapter markers and key moment timestamps.
  </p>

  <h3>Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Automatic timestamp generation for YouTube videos</li>
    <li>AI-powered video content analysis using Google Gemini</li>
    <li>Chapter marker creation for improved video navigation</li>
    <li>Key moment detection and summarization</li>
    <li>Video accessibility enhancement through structured timestamps</li>
    <li>Public feed of generated timestamps for community browsing</li>
    <li>Leaderboard system for most active contributors</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Usage Instructions</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>User provides a YouTube video URL in the input field</li>
    <li>Optional: User can provide a username for attribution</li>
    <li>System analyzes video content using AI (typically 2-5 minutes)</li>
    <li>Generated timestamps are displayed and saved to public feed</li>
    <li>Timestamps include time markers and descriptive text for each key moment</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Technical Capabilities</h3>
  <p>
    The application can process any public YouTube video URL and generate meaningful timestamps that identify important segments, topic changes, and key moments within the video content.
  </p>
</div>

